parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Passlock anti-theft system can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, which can lead to safety risks, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the Passlock system activates without intervention
and the vehicle will not start after a 10-minute wait.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical ignition system can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded, which can lead to safety risks, especially in emergency situations.
symptoms: The vehicle will not start
the ignition system fails to operate
and the vehicle will not crank.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light switch can cause the brake lights to not function, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The brake lights do not illuminate when the brake pedal is pressed
including the top lamp above the back window.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, which can increase the risk of injuries and fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light is on
the airbag system is not functioning properly
and the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the blower motor can cause a fire hazard, which can increase the risk of injuries and fatalities.
symptoms: The blower motor stops working
smoke and a pungent odor emanate from the passenger side
and the connector on the blower motor is melted.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to lose power, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates on its own
the vehicle stops while cruise control is on
and the throttle body needs to be cleaned.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause a fire hazard, which can increase the risk of injuries and fatalities.
symptoms: The wiring harness is damaged
wires are broken
and the airbag light is on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TPMS can cause the vehicle to lose tire pressure, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The TPMS fails and flashes continuously.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear brake drums can cause the vehicle to slow down but not stop, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pedal becomes hard to apply
the vehicle slows down but does not stop
the ABS light comes on
the brakes drag and squeal
the rear wheels spin
and the vehicle exhibits temporary loss of brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause the brake pedal to become hard to apply, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brake pedal becomes hard to apply
the vehicle slows down but does not stop
the ABS light comes on
and the brakes fail to engage properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical brake system can cause the brakes to drag and squeal, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The brakes drag and squeal
the rear wheels spin
the vehicle exhibits temporary loss of brakes
and the ABS light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front brake pads can cause the brake pads to emit a fine fiber-like material, which can enter the passenger cabin and cause respiratory issues.
symptoms: The front brake pads emit a fine fiber-like material
which gets on the front wheels
fender
and rocker panel
and enters the passenger cabin.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can result in the airbags not deploying in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard is illuminated
the airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash
the seat belt tensioner is not operating
the OnStar system does not make an emergency call.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to not retract properly, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The seat belt does not retract properly
the airbag warning light on the dashboard is illuminated
the seat belt tensioner is not operating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause the airbag system to malfunction, which can lead to serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard is illuminated
the airbags do not deploy in the event of a crash
broken wires in the harness between the door and body.
